<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Pizza AR Menu</title>
  <script type="module" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/model-viewer/3.4.0/model-viewer.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { background: #111; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: white; }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e);
      padding: 15px; text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    .header p { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.9; }
    model-viewer {
      width: 100%;
      height: 70vh;
      background: #111;
      --poster-color: #111;
    }
    .info {
      background: #222;
      margin: 10px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff6b35;
    }
    .name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #ff6b35; }
    .desc { color: #aaa; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 5px; }
    .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 12px; }
    .price { font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #f7931e; }
    .btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e);
      color: white; border: none;
      padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🍕 AR Pizza Menu</h1>
    <p>નીચે AR બટન દબાવો — Table પર Pizza જુઓ!</p>
  </div>

  <model-viewer
    src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/9173393556/pizza-ar/main/pizza%20(3).glb"
    ar
    ar-modes="scene-viewer webxr quick-look"
    ar-scale="fixed"
    camera-controls
    auto-rotate
    shadow-intensity="1"
    alt="Pizza 3D Model">
    <button slot="ar-button" style="
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 15px 35px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,53,0.5);
    ">
      🍕 Table પર જુઓ (AR)
    </button>
  </model-viewer>

  <div class="info">
    <div class="name">Margherita Pizza</div>
    <div class="desc">Fresh Tomato Sauce • Mozzarella Cheese • Basil Leaves</div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="price">₹299</div>
      <button class="btn">Order Now 🍕</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
